*Input Method Of Java*

1.Command Line Argument
    args[0] require
    package Import = No
    Exception :No
    Parsing require = yes

2.Buffered Reader/InputStream Reader
    package Import = java.io.*;
    Exception :IOException
    Parsing require = Yes

3.Scanner Class
    package Import = java.util.*;
    Exception : No
    Parsing require = No

4.System.console().readLine() Method
    package Import = No
    Exception : No
    Parsing require = Yes

*Hirarchy Of Java*

    Language
        package 
            Class   
                Method

*By Defaault package*
    java.lang.*;
    System is class Under this package

*Class*
    Member Variable
    Member Method
